    <h3>OneUptime GDPR Policy</h3>

    <p>OneUptime is operated by HackerBay, Inc. This page explains how we handle personal data for people in the EU, EEA, and UK, and the rights you have under the GDPR and UK GDPR.</p>
    <p>
        Topics:
        <br /> <br />
        - What data do we collect? <br />
